  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>On half board you'll have a buffet breakfast each morning with lots of choice. We love having our breakfast outside on the terrace on a sunny morning.</p>
<p>For dinner there's a delicious three-course meal with a choice of dishes. The Hotel Miramar's popular for its typical Italian food and even offers light lunches during the day (payable locally). Take advantage of the restaurant terrace which overlooks the lake. This is a great place to have your dinner or evening aperitivo.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
