  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Miramar is such a friendly hotel in the most fantastic location on the <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/sirmione" target="_blank" title="Sirmione">Sirmione</a> strip. It's right on the lakeside so you won't have far to go to dip your toes in the lake after a day walking around!</p>
<h2>Private beach</h2>
<p>It has its very own private beach with umbrellas and sun loungers which is ideal if you want a lazy day lounging by the water. The hotel's a little way out of the centre of Sirmione so it has a peaceful location on the peninsula which feels pretty exclusive to hotel guests.</p>
<h2>Exploring Sirmione's historic town centre</h2>
<p>You could spend hours exploring Sirmione's historic town centre which is less than a ten minute walk away from the hotel. It's full of bars, restaurants and shops and the beach is right on your doorstep! If you fancy stretching your legs, head for a lakeside stroll or walk through one of Sirmione's lovely parks.</p>
<h2>Fantastic views of Lake Garda</h2>
<p>The lake views from the hotel are incredible and it's got loads of view points, including the restaurant's outdoor terrace where you can relax with an Aperol or Hugo spritz. Make sure you get there in time for the sunset, it's a stunning way to wind down your day.</p>]]></description>
