  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms </strong>are spacious and sleep two people. They have a small balcony with a partial lake view.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> are around 27m² sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a balcony with lake views and an armchair or sofa. They're also equipped with tea &amp; coffee making facilities. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Shower stall</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A local tourist tax of approx. €1.50 per person per night is payable locally.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
